    <h3 > Polytechnic Course</h3>
    <p> Polytechnic is a diploma course for those who have already determined they want to pursue a technical career. These colleges offer diploma courses for 3 years, 2 years and 1 year. You can even choose to pursue a full-fledged engineering course after you complete your diploma course.</p>
   
    

